  "_metadata": {
    "version": 1,
    "data_as_of": "2026-04-27",
    "notes": "Baked-in constants for the ALICE estimator. Updates here when authoritative sources publish. Components are sourced individually so refresh cadence is per-source: HHS publishes FPL Jan, KFF publishes EHBS Oct, HUD publishes FMR Oct, USDA refreshes TFP each Oct, Census ACS 1-year publishes Sept, ACS 5-year publishes Dec. Replace via scripts/fetch_*.py when those land; v1 ships hardcoded values so the tool works out-of-the-box.",
    "methodology": "Mirrors United for ALICE (https://www.unitedforalice.org). Survival budget = housing + food + transport + healthcare + childcare + technology + taxes (effective). Computed per-household-size; cross-validated against United for ALICE published thresholds. % ALICE estimated by interpolating ACS B19001 bracketed counts between the household-size-weighted FPL and the household-size-weighted ALICE threshold."
  },
